								<ul class="feature-list">
									<li><strong>JWT Authentication:</strong> Stateless token-based authentication with 24-hour expiration</li>
									<li><strong>Role-based Access Control:</strong> HQ_ADMIN, STATE_MANAGER, STORE_MANAGER permissions</li>
									<li><strong>BCrypt Password Hashing:</strong> Secure credential storage with salt rounds</li>
									<li><strong>Spring Security 6:</strong> Comprehensive security framework with CSRF protection</li>
									<li><strong>CORS Configuration:</strong> Cross-origin resource sharing for frontend integration</li>
									<li><strong>Environment Variables:</strong> No hardcoded credentials in source code</li>
								</ul>
